Ness 

A Combo 
A = One Punch
Hold A = Taunt Punching ; Slightly Hold Forward Left or Right on the analog and tap A for: Forward Kicks 
A + A = Punch, Punch
A + A + A = Punch, Punch, Kick

Special Moves
B = Ness Firework
B + hold (left or right) = PK Fire
B + hold (down) = Ness Miracle Absorber 
B + navigate (up) = PK Thunder 

Smash Attacks
Hold A + Left or Right = Baseball Bat Swing 
Hold A + Down = Yo-Yo Smash Behind Ness
Hold A + Up = Forward Yo-Yo Smash 
